  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the almond flour, coconut oil, and honey.",
    "Mix until a dough forms, then press into a tart pan.",
    "Peel, core, and slice the apples, then mix with dried thyme, dried rosemary, and salt.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk the egg and vanilla extract, then add to the apple mixture.",
    "Pour the apple mixture into the tart shell and smooth the top.",
    "Bake for 35-40 minutes, or until the crust is golden brown and the apples are tender.",
    "Let cool for 10 minutes before serving."
